name: The Alien (skepticn8)
description:
Uh Oh! What's this? You've woken up to find yourself stranded on a strange planet. When you check your Planet Scanner, it says "Planet Earth." You look in the distance, you see scientists in their uniforms lining up ahead, they're trying to catch you. This begins your 10 Level long journey to your home planet!

Source Code - https://github.com/skepticn8/The-Alien
